text: Rolf Svensson (born 29 June 1935) is a Swedish archer. Svensson competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics, the 1976 Summer Olympics and the 1980 Summer Olympics.Rolf SvenssonRolf SVENSSON ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish archers Category:Olympians for Sweden Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
